Class WSDLDocument

java.lang.Object
  org.mcm.sws.wsdl.WSDLDocument
All Implemented Interfaces:
URIIdentifiable
public class WSDLDocument
extends java.lang.Object
implements URIIdentifiable

This class models the WSDL <Definitions> root-element (see also http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl12) and provides a parser method.
